data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to Windy Ridge, a charming community located in Grand Island. This spacious Savannah Model corner lot home, built in 2020, features an expansive kitchen island with additional seating, ample cabinet space, and stainless steel appliances. As you walk into the home, you’ll notice the tile throughout the main living areas and carpet in the bedrooms. The tray ceilings in the living room add to the spacious feel of the room. At Windy Ridge, you’ll have access to a tastefully designed community pool and playground. Plus, you’ll be just minutes away from shopping, dining, entertainment, and more.
